Compilation:

Use the makefile, just type: make

Usage:

tmcalc [ratios_list] [feh_calib_list] [Ares file]
Usage Example:
./tmcalc ratios_list.dat feh_calib_lines.dat HD20619.ares

Easy script:

TMCalc.bash


Usage:

TMCalc.bash [Ares file]
Usage Example:
./TMCalc.bash HD20619.ares


This can be directly used with the output file from ARES.
ARES Webpage: 
http://www.astro.up.pt/~sousasag/ares/

